{
  "stem": "14060.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were plenty of in-fights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was plenty of terrible things which certain people did to others for no reason at all-- just nastiness, you know-- which can, could cost them their lives.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And these didn't have to be kapos or blockaltestes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Human nature, anyway-- even amongst our own people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Let's be quite frank about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And these boys obviously were already five years under terrible conditions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And without exception, whatever Hasidic or religious background they came from, they were practically hated anything religious.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't forget, we came out four months earlier.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What do you mean, four months earlier?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Three months earlier, we went to shul regularly from on the Pesach, So for me, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they got to know-- first, they didn't like us right away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe because we were Hungarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that's beside the point.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't speak Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We spoke German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a somewhat tense atmosphere, insofar that we were not gladly accepted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even so, we were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But nothing terrible happened, except that they knew that we were religious.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They found out I had the [? seder. ?] And they went bonkers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They, they hated us after that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't report me, or anything-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "However, in September of 1944, when the Riga ghetto was liquidated, they brought 1,500 people back, men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And a transport was organized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And of course, the block-- the people who were in charge of individual block, being Jews there, inmates, they had the power to delegate whether you do this work, or whether you go into a transport, or you don't go into it.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, to go out of Buchenwald was not exactly helpful.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
